## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **vismodegib Erivedge 2012** = first FDA Hedgehog (SMO) inhibitor — laBCC + metastatic BCC. Hh pathway 의 임상 첫 paradigm. quantum-VQE 의 SMO 7TM pocket 이 직접 fit. muscle cramp + dysgeusia + alopecia 부작용 만성 복용 hindrance.
2. **sonidegib Odomzo 2015** = second SMO inhibitor laBCC. vismodegib 와 cross-resistance 부분적. SMO mutation D473H + W535L acquired resistance 가 두 약 모두 영향.
3. **cemiplimab Libtayo 2021** = first FDA PD-1 inhibitor BCC second-line (post-Hh). 2018 cSCC 첫 적응증 후 BCC 까지 확장. Hh-resistant 환자에 대안. quantum-VQE 의 PD-1 결합 fit.
4. **Mohs micrographic surgery 1L 표준** = high-risk + facial BCC 의 gold standard. complete margin assessment. 99% cure rate primary BCC. tissue-sparing cosmetic 우수.
5. **imiquimod 5% topical Aldara 2004 BCC** = TLR7 agonist topical immunomodulator — superficial BCC. 5-FU + PDT 와 함께 non-surgical 옵션. 전신 약 회피.
6. **photodynamic therapy ALA/MAL** = superficial + nodular BCC + AK field treatment. cosmetic 우수. multi-session 필요. quantum-VQE 의 photosensitizer 분자구조 fit.
7. **patidegib 2% / 4% topical research** = Gorlin syndrome BCC 1차예방 Phase III. PTCH1+/- 환자 lifelong 수많은 BCC 발생 → topical Hh inhibitor 가 systemic 부작용 회피 + chemoprevention.
8. **Gorlin (basal cell nevus) syndrome PTCH1+/-** = autosomal dominant. 평생 수백~수천 BCC + medulloblastoma + 골격이상 (cross-inherited_adult + pediatric_rare).
9. **SPF 30+ sunscreen + sun avoidance 1차예방** = UV-induced BCC + cSCC + melanoma 모두 1차예방 cornerstone (cross-melanoma_specific + cscc_specific + climate_health). 양자필름 sunscreen 차세대.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, BCC 임상 의미 한정. K-BCC 식약처 + 산정특례 framework framing 도 in-silico level.

